                     <interp inst="t17710410-25-person239" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known him three years; he is a hard-working, honest man. He desired to be examined at Sir<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177104100013"></xptr> 
            
                  <persName id="t17710410-25-person240">
                  John
                   Fielding
               <interp inst="t17710410-25-person240" type="surname" value="Fielding"></interp>
