                     <interp inst="t17710410-25-person240" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's. They said they had wounded him; he pulled off his clothes, and there was not the least mark of powder or shot.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17710410-25-person241">
                  Joseph
                   Richardson
               <interp inst="t17710410-25-person241" type="surname" value="Richardson"></interp>
