                     <interp inst="t17710410-25-person244" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have known the prisoner these eight years. He has a good character. I lived servant at major Wade's, he has been often there: I never missed any thing.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17710410-25-person245">
                  Sarah
                   Barnes
